{"text_id":30626,"tokens":["Although"," artificial"," neural"," networks"," have"," shown"," great"," promise"," in"," applications"," including"," computer"," vision"," and"," speech"," recognition",","," there"," remains"," considerable"," practical"," and"," theoretical"," difficulty"," in"," optimizing"," their"," parameters","."," The"," seemingly"," unreasonable"," effectiveness"," of"," neural"," networks"," (","SUN","N",")"," hypothesis",","," by"," contrast",","," suggests"," that"," the"," parameters"," of"," a"," neural"," network"," may"," be"," optimized"," with"," any"," reasonable"," search"," procedure","."," Here",","," we"," show"," that"," SUN","N"," can"," be"," used"," to"," optimize"," neural"," networks"," subject"," to"," syntactic"," regular","ities"," in"," the"," network","'","s"," topology",","," and"," that"," this"," approach"," leads"," to"," a"," systematic"," improvement"," in"," the"," performance"," of"," neural"," networks","."," Synt","ac","tically"," constrained"," networks"," are"," ","8","-","1","5"," faster"," to"," train",","," have"," fewer"," local"," minima",","," and"," are"," ","1","0","-","3","0"," more"," effective","."," A"," class"," of"," methods"," is"," introduced"," to"," automatically"," find"," syntactic"," regular","ities"," in"," neural"," networks","."," A"," regularity","-","sensitive"," network"," is"," demonstrated"," to"," achieve"," the"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," performance"," on"," a"," simple"," optical"," character"," recognition"," task","."," We"," also"," show"," that"," networks"," with"," less"," synt","ac","tically"," regular"," topology"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," have"," better"," local"," minima",","," and"," that"," the"," SUN","N"," hypothesis"," may"," not"," be"," valid"," for"," all"," types"," of"," networks","."," The"," results"," suggest"," that"," the"," SUN","N"," hypothesis"," may"," be"," applicable"," to"," networks"," of"," any"," structure"," that"," can"," be"," represented"," by"," a"," directed"," graph","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"7B","label":1}